QA Session and Seddion-App Timeout and Keep-Alive

1.  Add "env.db.server.name=localhost" to 
    /tecsys-all-web-war/src/main/resources/Developer.properties

2.  Edit com.tecsys.meta.ext.api.to.domain.MetaConfigAppInactivityTimeoutCode.java
      - Change "5" to "2"
        public static final MetaConfigAppInactivityTimeoutCode FIVEMINUTES = 
                new MetaConfigAppInactivityTimeoutCode("2", null);

3.  Edit com.tecsys.meta.ext.api.to.domain.MetaConfigTimeoutCode.java
      - Change "30" to "5"
        public static final MetaConfigTimeoutCode THIRTYMINUTES = 
                new MetaConfigTimeoutCode("5", null);

4.  Go to md_timer, and active the timer 'meta_ums_session_cleanup'

5.  Go to sys_mon
      - Start all Timers
      - Start queue 'meta_generic'

6.  Modify database directly 

select * from md_domain_value where domain_name='config_app_inactivity_timeout'
update md_domain_value set accepted_value=2 where domain_name='config_app_inactivity_timeout' and accepted_value=5

 

select * from md_domain_value where domain_name='config_timeout'
update md_domain_value set accepted_value=5 where domain_name='config_timeout' and accepted_value=30

 

update md_config set app_inactivity_timeout = 2;

7.  Restar portal